metadata.name: SYSTEMA. ONE
metadata.description:
In the first artwork of the "Systema" series, I embark on a research journey, seeking to unravel the rules and, perhaps, instructions about the structure of this world. Nature serves as my primary source of inspiration. I strive to depict it in the form of diagrams, in search of answers to my questions.

"SYSTEMA. ONE"
9449 × 9449
2023
